snippet.title: Quiplash 3 Official Teaser | The Jackbox Party Pack 7
snippet.description:
The Jackbox Party Pack 7 is coming this fall to major digital platforms.

To learn more about the first game in the pack (announced in this reveal video) go to http://bit.ly/2SVQDnM.
